      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEST ON MIRRA (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (27.94) in a Novice race at this track. Ready to return to form. LUCY'S DREAM (2) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Maiden winner three back (30.31) at Cannington over 520m. Well placed here and should do much better. ZERO SURF (4) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 488m behind SUNSET AUGUSTUS (28.11) in a Novice race. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. One of the better hopes. OFF SHORE (7) is worth including.",
